title: Akron Kitchen
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h1>The <em>"Akron Kitchen"</em> Project</h1>
    <p class="description">Weâ€™re a diverse group of locally-owned food businesses looking to bring
      a commercial kitchen to the Akron, Ohio area.</p>

    <div class="button-group">
      <a class="button button-primary" href="#what-we-want">Learn More About Us</a>
      <a class="button" href="https://www.facebook.com/akronkitchen/">Follow Us On Facebook</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container" id="what-we-want">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
      <h2 class="title">What We Want</h2>
      <p class="description">Our main goal is to help bring a commercial kitchen to
        the Akron area so that our local food community has a safe and
        licensed facility to cook food, produce products, and teach classes.</p>

      <p>Our community also provides a network to become introduced to Akron's
        food production scene. We have a Facebook group where we discuss
        local laws &amp; regulations, talk about interesting events, and help
        to connect people to other organizations and businesses.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr>

<section class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
      <h2 class="title">What We're Doing</h2>
      <p class="description">To justify the idea, we've already started collecting information about:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>Potential kitchen renters</li>
        <li>Existing kitchens for rent</li>
        <li>Information about local food organizations</li>
      </ul>

      <p><em>The information we collect is available to interested parties
            who can help us achieve our goals.</em></p>
      <p><a class="icon icon-left arrow-down" href="https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=0B5_MnDA-y-zdZXlIR0lPYjBMVWM&usp=sharing">Download Data</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr>

<section class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
      <h2 class="title">Get Involved</h2>
      <p class="description">We meet once a month to keep in touch, share information,
        and decide what our next steps will be.</p>

      <p>
        <a class="icon icon-left arrow-right uppercase" href="https://www.facebook.com/akronkitchen/events">View Upcoming Events</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr>

<section class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
      <h2 class="title">Who We Are</h2>
      <p class="description">We're made up of Akron's finest food entrepreneurs,
        caterers, restaurant owners, local growers, and area food organizations.
        Here are just a few of the people making things happen.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <ul class="row organizers clearfix">
    <% data.members.each do |name, member| %>
      <li>
        <% if member.url %>
          <a href="<%= member.url %>">
            <img alt="<%= name %>" src="<%= image_path(member.image) %>">
          </a>
        <% else %>
          <img alt="<%= name %>" src="<%= image_path(member.image) %>">
        <% end %>

        <h3>
          <% if member.url %>
            <a href="<%= member.url %>"><%= name %></a>
          <% else %>
            <%= name %>
          <% end %>
        </h3>

        <p><%= member.description %></p>
      </li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>

  <div class="text-center">
    <p>Interested in helping us out? Join the conversation as part of our
      private Facebook group.</p>
    <a class="button button-primary" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/akronkitchen/">
      <span class="icon icon-right chevron-right">Join Our Group</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <h4>Sharing is Caring</h4>
        <p>Please share our organization with your network to expand our reach.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-2">
        <h4>Get In Touch</h4>
        <ul class="contact-list">
          <li><a href="mailto:info@akronkitchen.org">info@akronkitchen.org</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/akronkitchen/">Facebook Page</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/akronkitchen/">Facebook Group</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="copyright">Copyright &copy; Akron Kitchen, <%= Time.now.year %></p>
  </div>
</footer>
